  "detailed_description": "Crossʀoad OS is a short, experimental adventure/puzzle game about navigating an unsettling operating system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783800/extras/9b7746abadd970ed33823abcd87b0725.poster.avif?t=1760360971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783800/extras/9b7746abadd970ed33823abcd87b0725.webm?t=1760360971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783800/extras/9b7746abadd970ed33823abcd87b0725.mp4?t=1760360971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unique Vibes</strong><br>The hum of a dusty CRT monitor fills the air as you wander the decaying partitions of this archaic operating system.<br></li><li><strong>Approachable Puzzles</strong><br>Short, sweet and accessible challenges for newcomers or experienced puzzle players.<br></li><li><strong>Explore</strong><br>Crawl through dungeon-like spaces, discovering clues, items and abilities to find out what's across the road.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783800/extras/db151cc73d1d8c929a8b4b1e3ed36595.poster.avif?t=1760360971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783800/extras/db151cc73d1d8c929a8b4b1e3ed36595.webm?t=1760360971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783800/extras/db151cc73d1d8c929a8b4b1e3ed36595.mp4?t=1760360971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><i>\"Experience horror worse than using Windows.\"</i><br>- Linux user",
